Fixes: https://github.com/xamarin/xamarin-android/issues/2864

Turn `Android.Security.Keystore.KeyStorePurpose` into a `[Flags]`
enumeration, so that tools like ReSharper don't emit warnings when
bitwise-`|`ing values together:

	var builder = new KeyGenParameterSpec.Builder (alias, KeyStorePurpose.Encrypt | KeyStorePurpose.Decrypt);
	// No warning from ReSharper!

